==Dutch==

===Verb===
'''baren'''
# To [[bear]]; to [[give birth]] to.
#: ''Zij heeft een zoon gebaard.'' &mdash; She has born a son.
# To [[cause]]; to [[bring about]].
#: ''Dit baart me zorgen.'' &mdash; This worries me (literally: "This causes worries to me").

